---
title: Peanutty Indonesian-Inspired Stir-Fry With Green Onion Jasmine Rice
description: Our sweet, peanutty sauce is the star of this meal! Stir-fried carrots, zucchini and chicken tenders are all tossed in this scrumptious sauce, then served over pillowy jasmine rice to catch every last drop of flavour.
